Lesson 3-7+ 2015-12-27A
Clone: A copy of a repository from GitHub to your local drive. 
Forking is cloning IN GITHUB with notification given to the original that a copy was made. 
Branch offshoot of the current master or other branch that must be committed in order to be 
accessible.


