Need to work with GIT FETCH

What is the benefit of having a copy of the last known state of the remote stored locally?
Can work on it offline then fetch/merge or pull others changes down L8R.

X 

How would you collaborate without using Git or GitHub? What would be easier, and what would be harder ?
Sneaker net or Email- ONLY one person working on a file at a time. Version control would be more difficult.
It might be slower as ONLY one person working on a file at a time.